spell.64

entangle:
When this spell is cast on a monster, that monster can no 
longer block, follow or flee.  

Only three classes, a mage, a druid or an assassin, are capable 
of casting this spell.  However, any class can use the entangle 
wand or recite the scroll to use its magic against a monster.

For Mages and Druids
MP cost: 10

For an Assassin:
MP cost: 15      Syntax: cast entangle <target>
